Alphatec Holdings, Inc. »
Alphatec Holdings, Inc. engages in the design, development, and promotion of products for the surgical treatment of spine disorders. Its products include spinal fixation, universal spacer, anterior cervical plate, and MIS posterior fixation system. It operates through the United States and International geographical segments. The company was founded on March 4, 2005 and is headquartered in Carlsbad, CA.




